<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> Coelho do Mato</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">L&aacute; no meio do mato africano, o coelho goza de muita fama. &Eacute; considerado o mais esperto bicho de quatro patas e um dos mais velozes n&atilde;o s&oacute; a correr como a pensar. Um <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[43],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">portento</a>.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Pois aconteceu que um velho le&atilde;o come&ccedil;ou a rondar a toca do coelho, guloso pelos <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[44],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">laparotos</a> tenros que, l&aacute; dentro, se preparavam para deitar as orelhas de fora.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> E que &aacute;vidos que eles estavam por sair da toca!
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Por enquanto, ainda &eacute; cedo - dizia a m&atilde;e coelha para os impacientes coelhinhos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Eles n&atilde;o paravam quietos.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Queriam vir para a rua, queriam respirar o fresco da manh&atilde;, <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[45],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">tasquinhar</a> as ervinhas novas, cabriolar, correr, saltar...
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Por enquanto, ainda &eacute; cedo - repetia a coelha, j&aacute; com o p&ecirc;lo em p&eacute; de tanto os aturar. - E se voc&ecirc;s continuam a portar-se mal, eu chamo o le&atilde;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%"> 	O velho le&atilde;o, que isto ouviu, acreditou que era a s&eacute;rio e ficou &agrave; espera que o chamassem. J&aacute; n&atilde;o tinha for&ccedil;as para grandes ca&ccedil;adas e preferia que o servissem, como nos restaurantes. A sonhar que estava &agrave; mesa, adormeceu e continuou a sonhar com coelho guisado.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O pai coelho, que vinha a entrar na toca, estranhou a sentinela &agrave; porta e, assim que se viu no meio da sua querida fam&iacute;lia, segredou para a mulher:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Temos visitas indesej&aacute;veis, mas vamos p&ocirc;-las a andar. Tu p&otilde;e as crian&ccedil;as a chorar, num grande berreiro.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Tabefe para a esquerda, tabefe para a direita e os <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[44],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">laparotos</a> desataram a chorar.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Tudo para bem deles.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O le&atilde;o, c&aacute; fora, acordou com a berraria. "Devem estar a chamar-me, n&atilde;o tarda", pensou. E p&ocirc;s-se &agrave; escuta.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mas o que ouviu arrepiou-lhe a juba.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Ouviu isto:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Pai Coelho: Porque &eacute; que os mi&uacute;dos est&atilde;o a chorar?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">M&atilde;e Coelha: Naturalmente, t&ecirc;m fome.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Pai Coelho: E tu n&atilde;o lhes deste o resto do f&iacute;gado de le&atilde;o que eu trouxe?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">M&atilde;e Coelha: Eles dizem que j&aacute; est&atilde;o fartos de comer f&iacute;gado de le&atilde;o e miolos de le&atilde;o e bifes de le&atilde;o. Por isso choram.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Claro que esta conversa em altos gritos era toda combinada entre o coelho e a coelha, mas o velho le&atilde;o n&atilde;o sabia e assustou-se. Assustou-se e fugiu, com rabo entre as pernas.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">"Aquela coisa de me chamarem devia ser uma cilada, uma armadilha", pensava o le&atilde;o. "T&atilde;o cedo n&atilde;o me apanham a escutar &agrave;s portas".</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=11&Dia=06','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
